DESCRIPTION: Given a valid token, it generates a new one.



Type: GET



INPUT:
None, only the bearer token is required.



RETURNS:
{
    "token": ... ,
    "user": ...
}

"token" -> string
"user" -> string



ERRORS:
400 (Bad request)
    Cause: Malformed JSON

401 (Unauthorized)
    Cause: Bad credentials

500 (Internal server error)
    Cause: Internal error
